# Task 3 – Project Workflow

## Project
Credit Card Approval Prediction Using Machine Learning

## Objective

Define the end-to-end workflow of the Credit Card Approval Prediction project, covering data collection, preprocessing, model development, evaluation, and deployment.

## Workflow

1. Environment Setup
2. Data Collection
3. Data Analysis
4. Data Visualization
5. Data Preprocessing
6. Feature Engineering
7. Model Building
8. Model Evaluation
9. Best Model Selection
10. Flask Application Development
11. Real-Time Prediction

## Machine Learning Models

- Logistic Regression
- Decision Tree
- Random Forest
- XGBoost

## Technologies Used

- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn
- Scikit-learn
- XGBoost
- Flask
- HTML/CSS

## Outcome

A complete machine learning pipeline that predicts credit card approval status using applicant information and deploys the best-performing model through a Flask web application.

## Conclusion

The structured workflow ensures efficient data processing, accurate model training, and successful deployment for real-time credit card approval prediction.
